content: thearyanag: Made significant contributions to the Solana Agent Kit with one large merged PR (#2458) that added over 200k lines while removing 56k lines across 2471 files. Currently has two open PRs (#1628 and #3037) related to the Solana Agent Kit integration. Activity was sporadic, concentrated on just 4 days this month, with a clear focus on feature development (64% of contributions) primarily involving code (70%) and configuration files (22%).
